metadata.name: Treachery, Level 9 - Ben Dawson I ArtSect Gallery
metadata.description:
“I  can’t communicate beyond the limits of language. We have never had the language. We never will.”

Treachery, Level 9 of Ben Dawson's descent into the seven layers of inferno.

From the exhibition "Arbitrary Names Cannot Define Such Tastes" at ArtSect NFT Gallery in Hackney, London.
